{"tid":312680,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"哇屌，我無聊補返以前套魔劣，咁既片點解咁紅......","createTime":"2017-07-07T16:06:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-08T11:14:30.000Z","uid":75100,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eb1aeca84a52b6c3734b008cea2c6dd867782726","tid":312680,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T16:06:30.000Z","msg":"講真，真係無邊咩劇情特別吸引<br />\n<br />\n慣例啦，係魔法世界入面，男主角硬係要係體術高手啦，要與眾不同嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打架就打架啦，成日用D奇怪方法收人皮，搞到人暈低之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後男主角梗係萬能架啦，咩都識既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後個戰，我真係屌你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成間學校既中學生一直努力學緊d魔法，想飛啊，想增強力量啊，想射d攻擊性既野出黎，達也就威囉，領先全部人十世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一炮秒軍艦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係屋企做鍵盤戰士描敵人，都可以秒殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  見唔見到d同學O哂嘴啊大佬，你射一炮就秒天秒地，你D垃圾同學以後點敢同你玩啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"261100f8c5d09854f058d7bcfa5714ef56de0965","tid":312680,"uid":30745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T16:08:38.000Z","msg":"女女+男主角屈哂機，好啱毒撚睇"},{"pid":"177e90ba57f069454b2f123fad947c0c2975f2b9","tid":312680,"uid":1531,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T16:13:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第1 <br />\n套路劇情 有咩好爭論必要...<br />\n成段野套落第2套一樣講得<br />\n<br />\n第2<br />\n毒撚鍾意咪得囉..."},{"pid":"aafcd423b330f7dc7d9cb3381d540be8f4e267e5","tid":312680,"uid":34293,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T16:15:04.000Z","msg":"一拳超人為興趣一拳收人地皮就得...<br />\n司巴達也想保護人秒7人就唔得..."},{"pid":"e4424f12e9b8080e375d1730d494d2aa97dae3c1","tid":